âŒ **Large PRs** - Keep changes focused to <300 lines; larger PRs require justification in description
âŒ **Pushing without testing** - Run `make ci` first
âŒ **Accumulating changes** - Commit and push incrementally
âŒ **Force push** - Use `--force-with-lease` (safer)
âŒ **Merging yourself** - Wait for user approval
âŒ **Missing inline comments** - Check with `gh talk list threads`
